                     Graia iuuenca venit, quae se, patremque virum
                           
                              
                           
                           que
                        
                     
                  
                  
                     Perdidit, Io laetor, Graia iuuenca venit:
                  
                  
                     Hellen, thy sister Hellen, nay shee's thine:
                  Who could haue thought that Hector being slaine,
