               A song within together with the musicke.
               
                  Weepe, weepe you Argonauts,
                  Bewaile the day
                  That first to fatall Troy
                  You tooke your way.
                  Weepe Greece, weepe Greece,
                  Two Kings are dead,
                  
                     Argos, thou Argos, now a graue
